{"tid":2345321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（懷仔）羅馬欲補強鋒線火力！將與國米搶謝雲奴","createTime":"2020-12-29T11:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T12:00:31.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e1888f96696e3ec4f2f66dbfc219213663a32e0","tid":2345321,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:49:05.000Z","msg":"據《共和報》報導，羅馬將與國米競爭帕爾馬前鋒謝雲奴（Kouassi Gervinho）。<br />\n　　報導稱，帕爾馬前鋒謝雲奴是轉會市場上的肥豬肉，除了干地（Antonio Conte）執教的國際米蘭外，方錫卡（Fonseca）執教的羅馬亦對他感興趣。<br />\n　　羅馬教練方錫卡認為謝雲奴的技術特點與自己的戰術思想非常匹配，並認為謝雲奴的加盟能夠幫助紅狼軍團加強鋒線火力。此前，謝雲奴曾在2013年8月至2016年1月為羅馬效力。"},{"pid":"53b29a0641ca2610e31fa4c7a63b5e4ec5514ea1","tid":2345321,"uid":36497,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"廢物都有人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474fa0d58135cfda06b3b94b5e9cd1ba81c76d25","tid":2345321,"uid":72497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:50:13.000Z","msg":"雲加手下無若冰"},{"pid":"dd0e77ee9d3600324308e78a2ef354be62414cd1","tid":2345321,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53b29a0641ca2610e31fa4c7a63b5e4ec5514ea1","tid":2345321,"uid":36497,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"廢物都有人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />貪佢靚仔賣波衫"},{"pid":"69a9ec9ce2ffdca2abd35ffa12be029488256121","tid":2345321,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"干地咁鍾意垃圾既<br />\n咩摸西斯on99 依家又謝雲奴"},{"pid":"52b946dbca3f61081d7235a801b7f955f016f601","tid":2345321,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69a9ec9ce2ffdca2abd35ffa12be029488256121","tid":2345321,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyT